Description: Implements sophisticated clustering algorithms for variables using
    an object-oriented R6 architecture. The package provides three specialized
    clustering methods: hierarchical clustering (VAR_CAH), categorical data
    clustering (KmodesVarClust), and descendant clustering with PCA-based
    recursive division (VARCLUS). Features include flexible discretization
    parameters, comprehensive validation, and robust handling of various data
    types.
